  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study investigates the impact of the introduction of a surgical checklist on the
      incidence of complications and mortality within 30 days after surgery in patients scheduled
      for elective non-cardiac surgery. Patients scheduled for elective surgical procedures lasting
      longer than 20 minutes at are eligible. Surgery is performed in a single tertiary care
      center. Study design is an open trial before and after intervention (implementation of the
      checklist &quot;safe surgery saves lifes&quot;).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
